data.description: Spacious Family Compound just north of the IL/WI boarder with frontage/access on beautiful Lake Elizabeth. Panoramic views both indoors and out. This home could be ideal for a family with children or parents/grandparents needing their own living space either on the main level or in the walkout basement. The 2nd floor master suite with it's vaulted ceilings, exercise room, private bath with jetted tub and laundry facilities could be your private oasis. Entertain the whole crew in the kitchen/dining/living rooms on the main level which also includes two additional bedrooms and baths.  The walkout basement includes two bedrooms, game room, rec room, dry bar, office, full bath and storage space. Winter fun awaits in WI! Minutes from Wilmot Mountain Ski Resort!
